Class TeacherUserDetails

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.wise.portal.domain.authentication.impl.PersistentUserDetails

    @Entity
public class TeacherUserDetails
extends PersistentUserDetails
implements MutableUserDetails
    Implementation class of MutableUserDetails that uses an EJB3 compliant object persistence mechanism. UserDetails for a teacher in WISE Portal
